Global Road Construction and Maintenance Equipment Market Insights
Road Construction and Maintenance Equipment Market size was valued at USD 19.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 27.3 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Road Construction and Maintenance Equipment Market Overview
The global road construction and maintenance equipment market is valued at USD 22.8 billion in 2024 and is projected to reach USD 31.2 billion by 2032, growing at a CAGR of 4.5%. The demand for this equipment is driven by increasing urbanization, infrastructure development, and government investments in road maintenance. Furthermore, the rising demand for sustainable and efficient construction methods is fostering technological advancements in machinery, enhancing operational efficiency, and reducing environmental impact. The market’s growth trajectory is also supported by the growing adoption of automation and smart technologies in road construction machinery.

